<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= destination.name %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body class="<%= destination.name.toLowerCase()%>-bg">
    <header>
        <nav>
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/#contact">Contact</a> <!-- Fix: Added /#contact to redirect to home -->
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <h1>Welcome to <%= destination.name %></h1>
        <img src="/images/<%= destination.image %>" alt="<%= destination.name %>" class="destination-image">
        <p><%= destination.description %></p>
        <% if (destination.name === "Paris") { %>
        <p class="paris-description">
            Paris is a dream destination for both singles and couples. From romantic walks along the Seine to solo cafe adventures in Montmare, the city has a vibe for everyone. It's filled with charming streets, breathtaking art, and unforgettable wine. Whether you're falling in love or falling in love with yourself, Paris delivers. This magical city makes every moment feel cinematic.
        </p>
      <% } %>
      <% if (destination.name === "Tokyo") { %>
        <p class="paris-description">
        Tokyo is a vibrant fusion of tradition and technology. From peaceful temple strolls to neon-lit nights in Shibuya, the city offers experiences for both introspective solo travelers and adventurous couples. Its culture, cuisine, and fashion scenes are unmatched. Whether you’re sipping matcha in a serene garden or exploring a bustling anime district, Tokyo surprises you at every turn. It’s a place where ancient beauty meets futuristic dreams.
        </p>
        <% } %>
        <% if (destination.name === "Rome") { %>
            <p class="paris-description">
            Rome is a timeless escape where history and romance are always alive. Couples can stroll hand-in-hand through cobbled streets, while solo travelers lose themselves in ancient ruins and espresso bars. Every corner tells a story—whether it’s whispered by the Colosseum or sung by a street violinist in Trastevere. With candlelit pasta dinners and golden-hour fountains, the city creates its own kind of magic. Rome doesn’t just welcome you—it romances you.
            </p>
            <% } %>
            <% if (destination.name === "New York") { %>
                <p class="paris-description">
                New York is energy, ambition, and beauty all packed into one unforgettable skyline. For couples, it's rooftop views and Central Park kisses; for singles, it’s late-night diners, galleries, and the thrill of being alone but never lonely. Every block buzzes with possibility, creativity, and life. Whether you’re catching a Broadway show or wandering through SoHo, the city makes you feel unstoppable. New York isn’t just a place—it’s a pulse.
                </p>
                <% } %>
        
    
        <!-- Best Places for Dinner Section -->
        <section class="dinner">
            <h2>Best Places for Dinner in <%= destination.name %></h2>
            <ul>
                <% if (destination.name === "Paris") { %>
                    <li><strong>Le Meurice</strong> - A luxurious Michelin-star restaurant with elegant French cuisine.</li>
                    <li><strong>Septime</strong> - A trendy spot offering a creative take on Parisian dishes.</li>
                    <li><strong>L'Ambroisie</strong> - An exclusive dining experience with classic French flavors.</li>
                <% } else if (destination.name === "Tokyo") { %>
                    <li><strong>Tsuta</strong> - The first Michelin-starred ramen shop.</li>
                    <li><strong>Ginza Kojyu</strong> - A fine dining kaiseki experience.</li>
                    <li><strong>Sukiyabashi Jiro</strong> - A world-renowned sushi restaurant.</li>
                <% } else if (destination.name === "Rome") { %>
                    <li><strong>Roscioli</strong> - Famous for its classic Roman pasta dishes.</li>
                    <li><strong>La Pergola</strong> - A Michelin-starred restaurant with stunning views.</li>
                    <li><strong>Armando al Pantheon</strong> - An intimate trattoria near the Pantheon.</li>
                <% } else if (destination.name === "New York") { %>
                    <li><strong>Peter Luger Steakhouse</strong> - Iconic Brooklyn steakhouse.</li>
                    <li><strong>Le Bernardin</strong> - A high-end seafood restaurant.</li>
                    <li><strong>Katz’s Delicatessen</strong> - A legendary spot for pastrami sandwiches.</li>
                <% } %>
            </ul>
        </section>
    
        <!-- Best Places to Make Content Section -->
        <section class="content-places">
            <h2>Best Places to Make Content in <%= destination.name %></h2>
            <ul>
                <% if (destination.name === "Paris") { %>
                    <li><strong>TeamLab Borderless</strong> - A digital art museum with stunning visuals.</li>
                    <li><strong>Montmartre</strong> - A historic district full of charming cafes.</li>
                    <li><strong>Seine River</strong> - A beautiful spot for Parisian cityscapes.</li>
                <% } else if (destination.name === "Tokyo") { %>
                    <li><strong>Shibuya Crossing</strong> - One of the busiest crossings in the world.</li>
                    <li><strong>Akihabara</strong> - A hub for anime and tech content.</li>
                    <li><strong>Roppongi Hills</strong> - Amazing skyline views.</li>
                <% } else if (destination.name === "Rome") { %>
                    <li><strong>Colosseum</strong> - A must-have backdrop for history lovers.</li>
                    <li><strong>Trevi Fountain</strong> - One of the most photogenic spots in Rome.</li>
                    <li><strong>Piazza Navona</strong> - A lively square full of artistic inspiration.</li>
                <% } else if (destination.name === "New York") { %>
                    <li><strong>Times Square</strong> - Bright lights and city energy.</li>
                    <li><strong>Brooklyn Bridge</strong> - A stunning spot for skyline shots.</li>
                    <li><strong>Central Park</strong> - Beautiful scenery for all seasons.</li>
                <% } %>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <!-- Slideshow Section -->
<section class="slideshow">
    <h2>Explore <%= destination.name %></h2>
    <div class="slideshow-container">
        <% if (destination.name === "Paris") { %>
            <div class="slide fade"><img src="/images/paris1.jpg" alt="Paris View"></div>
            <div class="slide fade"><img src="/images/paris2.jpg" alt="Eiffel Tower"></div>
            <div class="slide fade"><img src="/images/paris3.jpg" alt="Louvre Museum"></div>
        <% } else if (destination.name === "Tokyo") { %>
            <div class="slide fade"><img src="/images/tokyo1.jpg" alt="Shibuya Crossing"></div>
            <div class="slide fade"><img src="/images/tokyo2.jpg" alt="Tokyo Tower"></div>
            <div class="slide fade"><img src="/images/tokyo3.jpg" alt="Akihabara"></div>
        <% } else if (destination.name === "Rome") { %>
            <div class="slide fade"><img src="/images/rome1.jpg" alt="Colosseum"></div>
            <div class="slide fade"><img src="/images/rome2.jpg" alt="Trevi Fountain"></div>
            <div class="slide fade"><img src="/images/rome3.jpg" alt="Pantheon"></div>
        <% } else if (destination.name === "New York") { %>
            <div class="slide fade"><img src="/images/ny1.jpg" alt="Times Square"></div>
            <div class="slide fade"><img src="/images/ny2.jpg" alt="Brooklyn Bridge"></div>
            <div class="slide fade"><img src="/images/ny3.jpg" alt="Central Park"></div>
        <% } %>

        <!-- Navigation Arrows -->
        <a class="prev" onclick="changeSlide(-1)">&#10094;</a>
        <a class="next" onclick="changeSlide(1)">&#10095;</a>
    </div>
</section>

    
        <!-- Gallery Section (Already added) -->
         <!-- Services Section -->
<section class="services">
    <h2>Check Out My Services</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Custom Itinerary Package:</strong> Get a personalized travel plan tailored to your needs.</li>
        <li><strong>Photographer Recommendation:</strong> Find the best local photographers to capture your moments.</li>
        <li><strong>Long Stay Guide:</strong> Tips and resources for extended stays in <%= destination.name %>.</li>
        <li><strong>Kid-Friendly Area Recommendations:</strong> Discover the best places for family-friendly fun.</li>
    </ul>
</section>
    
        <!-- Back to Home Button -->
        <div class="back-home">
            <a href="/" class="btn">Back to Home</a>
        </div>
    </main>
    
    
    
<footer>
<p>© 2025 Travel App | All Rights Reserved</p>
</footer>
<script src="/js/slideshow.js"></script>
</body>
</html>